  Linux Firmware
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Checkout the tree at
  https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/firmware/linux-firmware.git/tree/

  $ PKGNAME=linux-firmware-$(date +%Y%m%d)
  $ mkdir -pv $PKGNAME 
  $ cd $PKGNAME
  $ <<checkout git tree here>>
  $ cd ..
  $ tar -cJf ${PKGNAME}.tar.xz $PKGNAME
-->
